-- TMX CEO Kloet Still Expects Large Mergers, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-03-27T07:06:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-27/tmx-ceo-kloet-still-expects-large-mergers-handelsblatt-reports.html
TMX Group Inc. Chief Executive
Officer  Thomas Kloet  said large stock exchange mergers across
countries and continents were still possible, speaking in an in
an interview with  Handelsblatt .  Kloet said he is looking at acquisitions, and exchanges
must have a stronger presence in  Asia , the German newspaper
reported.  For Related News and Information:  -- Editor: Chris Peterson  To contact the reporter on this story:
